data.text: Lists the assassinations as well as the attempted assassinations carried out by Israel against Palestinians outside Palestine and includes the methods used in its killings. Sources include daily newspapers and Ronen Bergman’s Rise and Kill First: The Secret History of Israel's Targeted Assassinations (New York: Random House, 2018).
